@NODE AddFrames

ADDFRAMES    Alias [NumberOfFrames]

   This command will add frames to an anim *OR* a picture.
   If it's a picture, it will become an anim.

   If you do not give the number of frames to add, then 1
   frame will be added. Otherwise, as many as you state, or
   as many as memory will allow.

   NOTE: Anim must be in @{" LoadAll " LINK "LoadAll"} mode.

